											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="give ring back *DUPE* Mattis turns 180 to face the table of wares behind her. She feigns being busy for a beat and flashes a subtle hand signal to her right - where her partner is standing. This is the signal for her partner to pickpocket the player. Once the signal has been given, Mattis turns back around to face the player, having &quot;prepared&quot; the items for them to browse.&lt;Beau&gt;" />
